<subSubSection id="8F8F6511FFB4FFCAC4DF06E491EDFE4F" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C72A369AFFB4FFCAC4DF06E491EDFE4F" blockId="3.[151,1436,150,500]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC4DF06E49464FF52" bold="true" box="[199,335,150,176]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">Comments.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="00954D19FFB4FFCAC54D06E49622FF52" authority="Song &amp; Chai (1991)" authorityName="Song &amp; Chai" authorityYear="1991" box="[341,777,150,176]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Rhene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="biembolusa">
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC54D06E49709FF52" box="[341,546,150,176]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">Rhene biembolusa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC63006E49622FF52" author="Song, D. X. &amp; Chai, J. Y." box="[552,777,150,176]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" pagination="13 - 30" refId="ref8188" refString="Song, D. X. &amp; Chai, J. Y. (1991) New species and new records of the family Salticidae from Hainan, China (Arachnida: Araneae). In: Qian, Y., Zhao, E. M. &amp; Zhao, K. T. (Eds.), Animal Science Research. China Forestry Publishing House, Beijing, pp. 13 - 30." type="book chapter" year="1991">Song &amp; Chai (1991)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was described based on a 
<typeStatus id="182E8838FFB4FFCAC03506E491A4FF52" box="[1069,1167,150,176]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">holotype</typeStatus>
male from Bawangling, 
<collectingRegion id="0551F878FFB4FFCAC48F06C895C0FF36" box="[151,235,186,212]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">Hainan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="BF82760AFFB4FFCAC4EE06C89416FF36" box="[246,317,186,212]" name="China" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">China</collectingCountry>
. The species was later discovered from mainland 
<collectingCountry id="BF82760AFFB4FFCAC77206C89686FF36" box="[874,941,186,212]" name="China" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">China</collectingCountry>
and both sexes were illustrated (
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC10406C895F9FF1A" author="Peng, X. J. &amp; Xie, L. P. &amp; Kim, J. P." pageId="3" pageNumber="392" pagination="31 - 36" refId="ref7717" refString="Peng, X. J., Xie, L. P. &amp; Kim, J. P. (1994) Descriptions of three species of genera Dendryphantes and Rhene from China (Araneae: Salticidae). Korean Arachnology, 10, 31 - 36." type="journal article" year="1994">
Peng 
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC14506C990A5FF36" box="[1373,1422,186,212]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">et al</emphasis>
., 1994
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC4F806AC948DFF1A" author="Song, D. X. &amp; Zhu, M. S. &amp; Chen, J." box="[224,422,222,249]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" refId="ref8265" refString="Song, D. X., Zhu, M. S. &amp; Chen, J. (1999) The spiders of China. Hebei Science and Technology Publishing House, Shijiazhuang, 640 pp." type="book" year="1999">
Song 
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC53A06AD947EFF1A" box="[290,341,222,248]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">et al</emphasis>
., 1999
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC5AC06AD9713FF1A" author="Peng, X. J." box="[436,568,222,249]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" refId="ref7766" refString="Peng, X. J. (2020) Fauna Sinica, Invertebrata 53, Arachnida: Araneae: Salticidae. Science Press, Beijing, 612 pp." type="book" year="2020">Peng, 2020</bibRefCitation>
). Based on the original and subsequent illustrations, the species shows clear resemblance in genital morphology to 
<taxonomicName id="00954D19FFB4FFCAC651077197C4FEFE" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1902" box="[585,751,258,284]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Rhene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavicomans">
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC651077197C4FEFE" box="[585,751,258,284]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">R. flavicomans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The male palp with short, ventrally curved embolus accompanied with slightly broad terminal apophysis resembling the embolus; epigyne with medially placed pair of oval openings; copulatory ducts broad, subparallel (cf. 
<figureCitation id="5FAE2A1FFFB4FFCAC6D50738961AFE86" box="[717,817,330,356]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1858,1882]" captionTargetBox="[168,1423,194,1832]" captionTargetId="figure-19@2.[151,1436,181,1835]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Somatic and genitalia morphology of Rhene flavicomans Simon, 1902 from Kerala: 1—habitus, dorsal view; 2—ditto, lateral view; 3—left palp, ventral view; 4—ditto, retrolateral view. Scale bars: (3, 4) 0.1 mm, (1, 2) 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6450911" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6450911/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">Figs 1–4</figureCitation>
, illustrations in 
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC7FF0738900CFE86" author="Proszynski, J." box="[999,1319,330,356]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" pagination="1 - 177" refId="ref7795" refString="Proszynski, J. (1984) Atlas rysunkow diagnostycznych mniej znanych Salticidae (Araneae). Zeszyty Naukowe Wyzszej Szkoly Rolniczo-Pedagogicznej w Siedlcach, 2, 1 - 177." type="journal article" year="1984">Prószyński (1984: 119–121)</bibRefCitation>
, figs 
<quantity id="006D9B7FFFB4FFCAC17D07389586FE6A" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.54" metricValueMax="2.794" metricValueMin="2.286" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" unit="in" value="10.0" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="9.0">9–11 in</quantity>
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC4AC071C94A8FE6A" author="Jastrzebski, P." box="[180,387,366,392]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" pagination="45 - 56" refId="ref7447" refString="Jastrzebski, P. (1997) Salticidae from the Himalayas. Genus Rhene Thorell, 1869 (Araneae: Salticidae). Entomologica Basiliensis, 20, 45 - 56." type="journal article" year="1997">Jastrzębski (1997)</bibRefCitation>
, figs 14A–E in 
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC62C071C9630FE6A" author="Song, D. X. &amp; Chai, J. Y." box="[564,795,366,392]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" pagination="13 - 30" refId="ref8188" refString="Song, D. X. &amp; Chai, J. Y. (1991) New species and new records of the family Salticidae from Hainan, China (Arachnida: Araneae). In: Qian, Y., Zhao, E. M. &amp; Zhao, K. T. (Eds.), Animal Science Research. China Forestry Publishing House, Beijing, pp. 13 - 30." type="book chapter" year="1991">Song &amp; Chai (1991)</bibRefCitation>
, figs 
<quantity id="006D9B7FFFB4FFCAC740071C968BFE6A" box="[856,928,366,393]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.778" metricValueMax="2.286" metricValueMin="1.27" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" unit="in" value="7.0" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="5.0">5–9 in</quantity>
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC7BF071D915BFE6A" author="Peng, X. J. &amp; Xie, L. P. &amp; Kim, J. P." box="[935,1136,366,393]" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" pagination="31 - 36" refId="ref7717" refString="Peng, X. J., Xie, L. P. &amp; Kim, J. P. (1994) Descriptions of three species of genera Dendryphantes and Rhene from China (Araneae: Salticidae). Korean Arachnology, 10, 31 - 36." type="journal article" year="1994">
Peng 
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC7FE071D913CFE6A" box="[998,1047,366,392]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">et al</emphasis>
. (1994)
</bibRefCitation>
and figs 280a–i in 
<bibRefCitation id="A3044B6BFFB4FFCAC151071D9439FE4E" author="Peng, X. J." pageId="3" pageNumber="392" refId="ref7766" refString="Peng, X. J. (2020) Fauna Sinica, Invertebrata 53, Arachnida: Araneae: Salticidae. Science Press, Beijing, 612 pp." type="book" year="2020">
Peng 
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC190071D9586FE4E" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">et al</emphasis>
. (2020))
</bibRefCitation>
. Therefore, here 
<taxonomicName id="00954D19FFB4FFCAC5C807E1975BFE4E" authorityName="Song &amp; Chai" authorityYear="1991" box="[464,624,402,428]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Rhene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="biembolusa">
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC5C807E1975BFE4E" box="[464,624,402,428]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">R. biembolusa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is considered as a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="00954D19FFB4FFCAC00107E19194FE4E" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1902" box="[1049,1215,402,428]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Rhene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="392" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavicomans">
<emphasis id="F5E1EA88FFB4FFCAC00107E19194FE4E" box="[1049,1215,402,428]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="392">R. flavicomans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
